        ('I love Exchange!','Exchange LA is one of the popular dance clubs in LA. It usually has well known DJs playing! They have a guest list line available almost every night so you can get in for free. I usually pay for my ticket because I do not want to get there before 10:30pm. If you go for the DJ and hear about it early enough, the tickets can range to $20-30 depending on the DJ.','https://d34ojwe46rt1wp.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/exchangela.jpg');